            <p>To the maximum extent permitted by law, Honest Drain &amp; Sewer LLC is not liable for indirect, incidental, consequential, special, or punitive damages, including loss of use, lost income, loss of business, inconvenience, emotional distress, or damages resulting from pre-existing conditions, hidden defects, or conditions outside the company's control.</p>
            <p>Nothing in these Terms &amp; Conditions limits liability for gross negligence, intentional misconduct, or any liability that cannot legally be limited.</p>

