            <p>The customer agrees to hold harmless and indemnify Honest Drain &amp; Sewer LLC, its owner, employees, subcontractors, representatives, and agents from claims, damages, losses, liabilities, costs, and expenses arising from:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Pre-existing conditions</li>
