              <li>Customer-provided misinformation</li>
              <li>Lack of proper authorization</li>
              <li>Unsafe or inaccessible work areas</li>
              <li>Defective piping</li>
              <li>Improper prior repairs</li>
              <li>Root intrusion</li>
              <li>Grease buildup</li>
              <li>Collapsed or deteriorated lines</li>
              <li>Water, sewage, or contamination conditions not directly caused by Honest Drain &amp; Sewer LLC's negligence</li>
